    Assuming servos lined up on horizontal axis,
    and theta drawn counterclockwise and in radians.
    [L], [R]    : servo coordinates.
    [q]         : end effector.
    [A], [B]    : unactuated joints coordinates.
    t1, t2      : joint angles.

                        V [q = (x, y)]
                       / \
                      /   \
                     /     \
                    /       \
                   /         \
                  /           \
                 /             \
            [A] /               \ [B]
                \               /
                 \             /
                  \           /
                   \ t1      / t2
  [Origin] -------- [L] ----- [R]
  (0, 0)                                         ^ y
  |----------------->| = a                       |
  |--------------------------->| = b              --> x

    End effector space boundaries:

          [C2]                    [C3]
           ...                    ...
           ...          V  [q]    ...
           ...         / \        ...
           ...                    ...
           ...       ... ...      ...
           ...                    ...
          [C1]      [L]   [R]     [C4]
*/
